    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, pampered in a heated garage and kept in flawless, showroom-ready condition. Not a single scratch, dent, or speck of dust\u2014it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line! If you\u2019re looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is your dream ride. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
