    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-grade vehicle that has been meticulously preserved. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional ceramic coating, with absolutely zero stone chips, scratches, or door dings. Inside, the cabin retains its original showroom freshness; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, and every electronic component functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a fully documented service history from day one and a bone-dry undercarriage. Garage-kept under a breathable cover and never driven in inclement weather, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year. It is a true time capsule for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
