    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is in stunning, flawless condition! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, keeping it spotless and garage-kept. It drives like a dream and honestly, you won\u2019t find a single scratch or hiccup anywhere. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy this beauty as much as I have. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
