      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2011 BMW M3 (E92) Competition Package (ZCP). This specimen features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering 414 hp through eight individual throttle bodies with a spine-tingling 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox, the mechanical engagement is unparalleled. The chassis benefits from ZCP-specific electronic damper control (EDC) mapping and a 10mm lower ride height, paired with staggered 19-inch Style 359M wheels. The exterior retains its factory depth with no discernible imperfections, while the interior leather remains supple with zero bolster wear. Mechanically flawless, with recent preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service documented. A true turn-key example for the discerning collector.",
